 in this collection carry IP67 or IP68 ratings, offering strong protection against dust and water for reliable use in harsh weather conditions.\"\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"@type\": \"Question\",\n      \"name\": \"Can I use a tow light bar for roadside assistance vehicles?\",\n      \"acceptedAnswer\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Answer\",\n        \"text\": \"Absolutely. These tow light bars are commonly used on roadside assistance and service vehicles, including units for tire changes, jump starts, and other breakdown services.\"\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"@type\": \"Question\",\n      \"name\": \"What flash patterns are available on your tow light bars?\",\n      \"acceptedAnswer\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Answer\",\n        \"text\": \"Most models include multiple programmable flash patterns such as alternating, sequential, and directional flashes, allowing you to choose the most effective pattern for roadside visibility.\"\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"@type\": \"Question\",\n      \"name\": \"Do your light bars support plug-and-play installation?\",\n      \"acceptedAnswer\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Answer\",\n        \"text\": \"Select tow light bars offer plug-and-play connectors for quicker setup, while others may require hardwiring into your vehicle’s power and control system.\"\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"@type\": \"Question\",\n      \"name\": \"Is there a warranty on tow truck light bars?\",\n      \"acceptedAnswer\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Answer\",\n        \"text\": \"Yes. Tow light bars typically include manufacturer warranties that range from one to five years, depending on the specific brand and model you choose.\"\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"@type\": \"Question\",\n      \"name\": \"Can I connect a tow light bar to my existing emergency lighting system?\",\n      \"acceptedAnswer\": {\n        \"@type\": \"Answer\",\n        \"text\": \"In most cases, yes. Many tow light bars can be integrated with auxiliary lighting systems and are compatible with popular controllers from brands like Feniex, SoundOff Signal, and Whelen.\"\n      }\n    }\n  ]\n}\n</script>"
